title: Kielsen V Cabinet
text:
The Fifth Cabinet of Kim Kielsen was the <a href="Government%20of%20Greenland">Government of Greenland</a>, in office between 5 October 2018 and 9 April 2019. It was a <a href="coalition">coalition</a> <a href="minority%20government">minority government</a> consisting of <a href="Forward%20%28Greenland%29">Siumut</a>, <a href="Atassut">Solidarity</a> and <a href="Nunatta%20Qitornai">Descendants of Our Country</a>.
List of ministers.
The Social Democratic Forward haD 6 ministers including the Premier. The Liberalistic Solidarity had 2 ministers. The Centrist party Descendants of Our Country had 1 minister.
